item.title: Bro, do you even lift?
item.description: ##03:13 Thursday 06 November 2014 JST## I don’t didn’t know what the meme “Bro, do you even lift?“ means (in fact, I thought “Bro” was part of it), but I wanted to title this entry with a letter early in the alphabet because my entries are sorted alphabetically (at the moment), and it’s related to Lift, specifically the Lift Open Coaching Program. Anyway, I tried logging in to their coaching seminar, but was unable.
